			<!-- icon and title -->
			<div class="smallfont">
				
				<strong>What should EQ1 steal from the competition?</strong>
			</div>
			<hr size="1" style="color:#330066" />
			<!-- / icon and title -->
		
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div>The smart money for sprucing up EQ1 is to implement EQ1 fixes that have been a long time coming.<br />
<br />
But in today's MBA-driven world, the more likely fixes will be ones ripped from EQ2 and WoW and that are seen as successful and easy to emulate.<br />
<br />
Since SOE is (faking?) listening again to the playerbase, what would <i>you</i> like to see snatched from EQ2 and WoW and added to EQ1? Be specific.<br />
<br />
(If you're on this board, you're presumed to like EQ1 and want it to succeed. Save cute &quot;stick a fork in it, it's done&quot; sorts of comments for other boards.)</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
